letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(20, 25, 30); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\">更新使用的是DB类的静态方法update()，</span><span style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(20, 25, 30); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\">第一个参数是sql语句，第二个参数是一个数组，数组里的元素分别对应sql语句里的问号。更新成功返回true。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); text-transform: none; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(20, 25, 30); -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(20, 25, 30); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(20, 25, 30); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\"></span></span></span></span></span></p><p><strong style=\"outline: 0px; font-weight: bold; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\">[php]</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a title=\"view plain\" class=\"ViewSource\" style=\"background-position: left top; margin: 0px 10px 0px 0px; padding: 1px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; width: 16px; height: 16px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-indent: -2000px; font-size: 9px; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; cursor: pointer; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-image: url(&quot;https://csdnimg.cn/release/phoenix/images/ico_plain.gif&quot;); background-repeat: no-repeat; background-color: inherit;\" href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/zls986992484/article/details/52824962#\">view plain</a><span style=\"outline: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a title=\"copy\" class=\"CopyToClipboard\" style=\"background-position: left top; margin: 0px 10px 0px 0px; padding: 1px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; width: 16px; height: 16px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-indent: -2000px; font-size: 9px; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; cursor: pointer; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-image: url(&quot;https://csdnimg.cn/release/phoenix/images/ico_copy.gif&quot;); background-repeat: no-repeat; background-color: inherit;\" href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/zls986992484/article/details/52824962#\">copy</a></span><span style=\"outline: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\"></span></p><ol class=\"dp-c list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\"><li><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: black; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\"><span class=\"vars\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(221, 0, 0); -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">$bool</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: black; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">=DB::update(</span><span class=\"string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: blue; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">&#39;update&nbsp;vipinfo&nbsp;set&nbsp;vip_fenshu=&nbsp;?&nbsp;where&nbsp;vip_ID=&nbsp;?&nbsp;&#39;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: black; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">,[700,5]);&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: black; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">var_dump(<span class=\"vars\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(221, 0, 0); -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">$bool</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: black; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">);&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class=\"comment\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(0, 130, 0); -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">//更新成功返回true</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: black; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p></li></ol><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">4. 删除操作</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); text-transform: none; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(20, 25, 30); -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(20, 25, 30); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(20, 25, 30); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(20, 25, 30); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\">删除使用的是DB类的静态方法delete()，<span style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(20, 25, 30); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\">第一个参数是sql语句，第二个参数是一个数组，数组里的元素分别对应sql语句里的问号。返回的是删除的行数。</span></span><br/></span></span></span></span></span></p><p><strong style=\"outline: 0px; font-weight: bold; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\">[php]</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a title=\"view plain\" class=\"ViewSource\" style=\"background-position: left top; margin: 0px 10px 0px 0px; padding: 1px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; width: 16px; height: 16px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-indent: -2000px; font-size: 9px; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; cursor: pointer; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-image: url(&quot;https://csdnimg.cn/release/phoenix/images/ico_plain.gif&quot;); background-repeat: no-repeat; background-color: inherit;\" href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/zls986992484/article/details/52824962#\">view plain</a><span style=\"outline: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a title=\"copy\" class=\"CopyToClipboard\" style=\"background-position: left top; margin: 0px 10px 0px 0px; padding: 1px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; width: 16px; height: 16px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-indent: -2000px; font-size: 9px; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; cursor: pointer; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-image: url(&quot;https://csdnimg.cn/release/phoenix/images/ico_copy.gif&quot;); background-repeat: no-repeat; background-color: inherit;\" href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/zls986992484/article/details/52824962#\">copy</a></span><span style=\"outline: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\"></span></p><ol class=\"dp-c list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\"><li><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: black; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\"><span class=\"vars\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(221, 0, 0); -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">$num</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: black; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">=DB::</span><span class=\"func\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: black; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">delete</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: black; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">(</span><span class=\"string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: blue; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">&#39;delete&nbsp;from&nbsp;vipinfo&nbsp;where&nbsp;vip_ID=&nbsp;?&#39;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: black; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">,[5]);&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: black; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\"><span class=\"func\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: black; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">echo</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: black; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"vars\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(221, 0, 0); -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">$num</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: black; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p></li></ol>', 1529056042, '白衣少侠', 0, 21);
INSERT INTO `blog_article_copy1` VALUES (2, 'Eloquent ORM —— 快速入门', 'ORM', '控制台', 'uploads/20180616102353625.jpg', '<h3 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.1; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; clear: both; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 500; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">1、简介</h3><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">Laravel 内置的 Eloquent ORM 提供了一个美观、简单的与数据库打交道的 ActiveRecord 实现，每张数据表都对应一个与该表进行交互的“模型”，模型允许你在表中进行数据查询，以及插入、更新、删除等操作。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">在开始之前，确保在<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">config/database.php</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>文件中配置好了数据库连接。更多关于数据库配置的信息，请查看<a style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box;\" href=\"http://laravelacademy.org/post/6947.html#toc_1\">文档</a>。</p><h3 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.1; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; clear: both; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 500; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">2、定义模型</h3><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">我们从创建一个 Eloquent 模型开始，模型通常位于<code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">app</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>目录下，你也可以将其放在其他可以被<code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">composer.json</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>文件自动加载的地方。所有Eloquent 模型都继承自<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">Illuminate\\Database\\Eloquent\\Model</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>类。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">创建模型实例最简单的办法就是使用<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box;\" href=\"http://laravelacademy.org/post/6842.html\">Artisan 命令</a><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">make:model</code>：</p><pre style=\"background: rgb(245, 245, 245); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 9.5px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.4285; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; overflow: auto; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; white-space: pre-wrap; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">php&nbsp;artisan&nbsp;make:model&nbsp;User</pre><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">如果你想要在生成模型时生成数据库迁移，可以使用<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">--migration</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>或<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">-m</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>选项：</p><pre style=\"background: rgb(245, 245, 245); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 9.5px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.4285; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; overflow: auto; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; white-space: pre-wrap; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">php&nbsp;artisan&nbsp;make:model&nbsp;User&nbsp;--migration\r\nphp&nbsp;artisan&nbsp;make:model&nbsp;User&nbsp;-m</pre><h4 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.1; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; clear: both; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 500; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">Eloquent 模型约定</h4><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">现在，让我们来看一个<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">Flight</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>模型类例子，我们将用该类获取和存取数据表<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">flights</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>中的信息：</p><pre style=\"background: rgb(245, 245, 245); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 9.5px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.4285; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; overflow: auto; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; white-space: pre-wrap; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">&lt;?php\r\n\r\nnamespace&nbsp;App;\r\n\r\nuse&nbsp;Illuminate\\Database\\Eloquent\\Model;\r\n\r\nclass&nbsp;Flight&nbsp;extends&nbsp;Model{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//\r\n}</pre><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box;\">表名</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">注意我们并没有告诉 Eloquent 我们的<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">Flight</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>模型使用哪张表。默认规则是模型类名的复数作为与其对应的表名，除非在模型类中明确指定了其它名称。所以，在本例中，Eloquent 认为<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">Flight</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>模型存储记录在<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">flights</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>表中。你也可以在模型中定义<code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">table</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>属性来指定自定义的表名：</p><pre style=\"background: rgb(245, 245, 245); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 9.5px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.4285; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; overflow: auto; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; white-space: pre-wrap; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">&lt;?php\r\n\r\nnamespace&nbsp;App;\r\n\r\nuse&nbsp;Illuminate\\Database\\Eloquent\\Model;\r\n\r\nclass&nbsp;Flight&nbsp;extends&nbsp;Model\r\n{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;/**\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;关联到模型的数据表\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;@var&nbsp;string\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*/\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;protected&nbsp;$table&nbsp;=&nbsp;&#39;my_flights&#39;;\r\n}</pre><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box;\">主键</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">Eloquent 默认每张表的主键名为<code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">id</code>，你可以在模型类中定义一个<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">$primaryKey</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>属性来覆盖该约定。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">此外，Eloquent 默认主键字段是自增的整型数据，这意味着主键将会被自动转化为<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">int</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>类型，如果你想要使用非自增或非数字类型主键，必须在对应模型中设置<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">$incrementing</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>属性为<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">false</code>。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box;\">时间戳</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">默认情况下，Eloquent 期望<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">created_at</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>和<code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">updated_at</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>已经存在于数据表中，如果你不想要这些 Laravel 自动管理的数据列，在模型类中设置<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">$timestamps</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>属性为<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">false</code>：</p><pre style=\"background: rgb(245, 245, 245); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 9.5px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.4285; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; overflow: auto; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; white-space: pre-wrap; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">&lt;?php\r\n\r\nnamespace&nbsp;App;\r\n\r\nuse&nbsp;Illuminate\\Database\\Eloquent\\Model;\r\n\r\nclass&nbsp;Flight&nbsp;extends&nbsp;Model\r\n{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;/**\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;表明模型是否应该被打上时间戳\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;@var&nbsp;bool\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*/\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;$timestamps&nbsp;=&nbsp;false;\r\n}</pre><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">如果你需要自定义时间戳格式，设置模型中的<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">$dateFormat</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>属性。该属性决定日期被如何存储到数据库中，以及模型被序列化为数组或 JSON 时日期的格式：</p><pre style=\"background: rgb(245, 245, 245); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 9.5px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.4285; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; overflow: auto; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; white-space: pre-wrap; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">&lt;?php\r\n\r\nnamespace&nbsp;App;\r\n\r\nuse&nbsp;Illuminate\\Database\\Eloquent\\Model;\r\n\r\nclass&nbsp;Flight&nbsp;extends&nbsp;Model\r\n{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;/**\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;模型日期列的存储格式\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;@var&nbsp;string\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*/\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;protected&nbsp;$dateFormat&nbsp;=&nbsp;&#39;U&#39;;\r\n}</pre><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">如果你需要自定义用于存储时间戳的字段名称，可以在模型中设置<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">CREATED_AT</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>和<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">UPDATED_AT</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>常量：</p><pre style=\"background: rgb(245, 245, 245); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 9.5px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.4285; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; overflow: auto; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; white-space: pre-wrap; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">&lt;?php\r\n\r\nclass&nbsp;Flight&nbsp;extends&nbsp;Model\r\n{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;const&nbsp;CREATED_AT&nbsp;=&nbsp;&#39;creation_date&#39;;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;const&nbsp;UPDATED_AT&nbsp;=&nbsp;&#39;last_update&#39;;\r\n}</pre><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box;\">数据库连接</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">默认情况下，所有的 Eloquent 模型使用应用配置中的默认数据库连接，如果你想要为模型指定不同的连接，可以通过<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">$connection</code><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>属性来设置：</p><pre style=\"background: rgb(245, 245, 245); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 9.5px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.4285; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; overflow: auto; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; white-space: pre-wrap; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">&lt;?php\r\n\r\nnamespace&nbsp;App;\r\n\r\nuse&nbsp;Illuminate\\Database\\Eloquent\\Model;\r\n\r\nclass&nbsp;Flight&nbsp;extends&nbsp;Model\r\n{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;/**\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;The&nbsp;connection&nbsp;name&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;model.\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;@var&nbsp;string\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*/\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;protected&nbsp;$connection&nbsp;=&nbsp;&#39;connection-name&#39;;\r\n}</pre><h3 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.1; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; clear: both; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 500; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">3、获取模型</h3><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">创建完模型及其关联的数据表后，就要准备从数据库中获取数据。将 Eloquent 模型看作功能强大的<a style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box;\" href=\"http://laravelacademy.org/post/6955.html\">查询构建器</a>，你可以使用它来流畅的查询与其关联的数据表。例如：</p><pre style=\"background: rgb(245, 245, 245); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 9.5px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.4285; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; overflow: auto; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; white-space: pre-wrap; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">&lt;?php\r\n\r\nuse&nbsp;App\\Flight;\r\n\r\n$flights&nbsp;=&nbsp;App\\Flight::all();\r\n\r\nforeach&nbsp;($flights&nbsp;as&nbsp;$flight)&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;$flight-&gt;name;\r\n}</pre><p>&nbsp;</p>', 1529057144, '白衣少侠', 0, 21);
INSERT INTO `blog_article_copy1` VALUES (3, '数据库 —— 查询构建器', '数据库', '注意：Laravel查询构建器使用PDO参数绑定来避免SQL注入攻击，不再需要过滤传递到绑定的字符串。', 'uploads/20180616112105968.jpg', '<h3 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.1; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; clear: both; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 500; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold; box-sizing: border-box;\">1、简介</strong></h3><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">数据库查询构建器提供了一个方便的、平滑的接口来创建和运行数据库查询。查询构建器可以用于执行应用中大部分数据库操作，并且能够在支持的所有数据库系统上工作。</p><blockquote style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 0px 5px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 10px 20px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-left-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; quotes: &quot;&quot; &quot;&quot;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; line-height: 1.25; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 300; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box;\">注意：Laravel查询构建器使用PDO参数绑定来避免SQL注入攻击，不再需要过滤传递到绑定的字符串。</p></blockquote><h3 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.1; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; clear: both; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 500; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold; box-sizing: border-box;\">2、获取结果集</strong></h3><h4 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.1; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; clear: both; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 500; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box;\">2.1 从一张表中取出所有行</strong></h4><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">在查询之前，使用<code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">DB</code>门面的<code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">table</code>方法，<code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">table</code>方法为给定表返回一个查询构建器，允许你在查询上链接更多约束条件并最终返回查询结果。在本例中，我们使用<code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">get</code>方法获取表中所有记录：</p><pre style=\"background: rgb(245, 245, 245); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 9.5px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.4285; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; overflow: auto; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; white-space: pre-wrap; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">&lt;?php\r\n\r\nnamespace&nbsp;App\\Http\\Controllers;\r\n\r\nuse&nbsp;DB;\r\nuse&nbsp;App\\Http\\Controllers\\Controller;\r\n\r\nclass&nbsp;UserController&nbsp;extends&nbsp;Controller{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;/**\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;显示用户列表\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;@return&nbsp;Response\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*/\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;index()\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$users&nbsp;=&nbsp;DB::table(&#39;users&#39;)-&gt;get();\r\n\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;view(&#39;user.index&#39;,&nbsp;[&#39;users&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;$users]);\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\r\n}</pre><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">和<a style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box;\" href=\"http://laravelacademy.org/post/124.html\">原生查询</a>一样，<code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">get</code>方法返回结果集的数据组，其中每一个结果都是PHP对象的<code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">StdClass</code>实例。你可以像访问对象的属性一样访问列的值：</p><pre style=\"background: rgb(245, 245, 245); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 9.5px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.4285; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; overflow: auto; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; white-space: pre-wrap; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">foreach&nbsp;($users&nbsp;as&nbsp;$user)&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;$user-&gt;name;\r\n}</pre><h4 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.1; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; clear: both; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 500; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box;\">2.2 从一张表中获取一行/一列</strong></h4><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">如果你只是想要从数据表中获取一行数据，可以使用<code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">first</code>方法，该方法将会返回单个<code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">StdClass</code>对象：</p><pre style=\"background: rgb(245, 245, 245); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 9.5px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.4285; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; overflow: auto; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; white-space: pre-wrap; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">$user&nbsp;=&nbsp;DB::table(&#39;users&#39;)-&gt;where(&#39;name&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;John&#39;)-&gt;first();\r\necho&nbsp;$user-&gt;name;</pre><h4 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.1; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; clear: both; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 500; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box;\">2.3 从一张表中获取组块结果集</strong></h4><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">如果你需要处理成千上百条数据库记录，可以考虑使用<code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">chunk</code>方法，该方法一次获取结果集的一小块，然后填充每一小块数据到要处理的闭包，该方法在编写处理大量数据库记录的<a style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box;\" href=\"http://laravelacademy.org/post/170.html\">Artisan命令</a>的时候非常有用。比如，我们可以将处理全部users表数据处理成一次处理100记录的小组块：</p><pre style=\"background: rgb(245, 245, 245); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 9.5px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.4285; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; overflow: auto; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; white-space: pre-wrap; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">DB::table(&#39;users&#39;)-&gt;chunk(100,&nbsp;function($users)&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;foreach&nbsp;($users&nbsp;as&nbsp;$user)&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\r\n});</pre><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">你可以通过从闭包函数中返回false来中止组块的运行：</p><pre style=\"background: rgb(245, 245, 245); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 9.5px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.4285; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; overflow: auto; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; white-space: pre-wrap; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">DB::table(&#39;users&#39;)-&gt;chunk(100,&nbsp;function($users)&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;处理结果集...\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;false;\r\n});</pre><h4 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.1; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; clear: both; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 500; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box;\">2.4 获取数据列值列表</strong></h4><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">如果想要获取包含单个列值的数组，可以使用<code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">lists</code>方法，在本例中，我们获取所有<code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">title</code>的数组：</p><pre style=\"background: rgb(245, 245, 245); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 9.5px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.4285; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; overflow: auto; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; white-space: pre-wrap; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">$titles&nbsp;=&nbsp;DB::table(&#39;roles&#39;)-&gt;lists(&#39;title&#39;);\r\n\r\nforeach&nbsp;($titles&nbsp;as&nbsp;$title)&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;$title;\r\n}</pre><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">在还可以在返回数组中为列值指定更多的自定义键（该自定义键必须是该表的其它字段列名，否则会报错）：</p><pre style=\"background: rgb(245, 245, 245); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 9.5px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.4285; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; overflow: auto; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; white-space: pre-wrap; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">$roles&nbsp;=&nbsp;DB::table(&#39;roles&#39;)-&gt;lists(&#39;title&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;name&#39;);\r\n\r\nforeach&nbsp;($roles&nbsp;as&nbsp;$name&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;$title)&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;$title;\r\n}</pre><h4 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.1; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; clear: both; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 500; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box;\">2.5 聚合函数</strong></h4><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">队列构建器还提供了很多聚合方法，比如<code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">count</code>,&nbsp;<code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">max</code>,&nbsp;<code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">min</code>,&nbsp;<code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">avg</code>, 和&nbsp;<code style=\"font: 12.6px/normal Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(244, 100, 95); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">sum</code>，你可以在构造查询之后调用这些方法：</p><pre style=\"background: rgb(245, 245, 245); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 9.5px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.4285; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; overflow: auto; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; white-space: pre-wrap; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">$users&nbsp;=&nbsp;DB::table(&#39;users&#39;)-&gt;count();\r\n$price&nbsp;=&nbsp;DB::table(&#39;orders&#39;)-&gt;max(&#39;price&#39;);</pre><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">当然，你可以联合其它查询字句和聚合函数来构建查询：</p><pre style=\"background: rgb(245, 245, 245); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 9.5px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.4285; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; overflow: auto; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; white-space: pre-wrap; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">$price&nbsp;=&nbsp;DB::table(&#39;orders&#39;)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;-&gt;where(&#39;finalized&#39;,&nbsp;1)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;-&gt;avg(&#39;price&#39;)</pre>', 1529116999, '白衣少侠', 0, 9);
INSERT INTO `blog_article_copy1` VALUES (5, 'laravel中的数组分页实现', '分页', 'laravel中的数组分页实现', 'uploads/default.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); text-transform: none; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">关于我假如我需要重新某个表中的数据，然后将整理出来的数据重新封装之后没有办法用laravel中的paginate分页了，我找到了一个方法链接大家可以去看看<a style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\" href=\"http://psampaz.github.io/custom-data-pagination-with-laravel-5/\" target=\"_blank\">http://psampaz.github.io/custom-data-pagination-with-laravel-5/</a>&nbsp;<br/>大概的写一下吧：</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 8px 16px 4px 56px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 22px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; position: relative; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-overflow-x: auto; -ms-overflow-y: hidden; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">use&nbsp;Illuminate\\Pagination\\LengthAwarePaginator;use&nbsp;Illuminate\\Support\\Collection;\r\n...$searchResults&nbsp;=&nbsp;[&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;item1&#39;,&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;item2&#39;,&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;item3&#39;,&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;item4&#39;,&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;item5&#39;,&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;item6&#39;,&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;item7&#39;,&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;item8&#39;,&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;item9&#39;,&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;item10&#39;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;];&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//获取当前的分页数，就是第6这样的\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$currentPage&nbsp;=&nbsp;LengthAwarePaginator::resolveCurrentPage();&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//实例化collect方法\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$collection&nbsp;=&nbsp;new&nbsp;Collection($searchResults);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//定义一下每页显示多少个数据\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$perPage&nbsp;=&nbsp;5;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//获取当前需要显示的数据列表\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$currentPageSearchResults&nbsp;=&nbsp;$collection-&gt;slice($currentPage&nbsp;*&nbsp;$perPage,&nbsp;$perPage)-&gt;all();&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//创建一个新的分页方法\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$paginatedSearchResults=&nbsp;new&nbsp;LengthAwarePaginator($currentPageSearchResults,&nbsp;count($collection),&nbsp;$perPage);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;view(&#39;search&#39;,&nbsp;[&#39;results&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;$paginatedSearchResults]);\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}123456789101112131415161718192021222324252627282930313233</pre><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); text-transform: none; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><br/></p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 8px 16px 4px 56px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 22px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; position: relative; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-overflow-x: auto; -ms-overflow-y: hidden; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">$paginatedSearchResults&nbsp;=&nbsp;$paginatedSearchResults-&gt;setPath(&#39;/myUrl/a&#39;);</pre><p><br/></p>', 1529136597, '白衣少侠', 0, 21);
INSERT INTO `blog_article_copy1` VALUES (6, 'Laravel数据库操作的三种方式（2）', '数据库', 'Laravel提供了3种操作数据库方式：DB facade（原始方式）、查询构造器和Eloquent ORM。', 'uploads/default.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); text-transform: none; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">二、数据库操作之查询构造器</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); text-transform: none; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">laravel查询构造器提供了方便流畅的接口，用来建立及执行数据库查找语法。使用了pdo参数绑定，使应用程序免于sql注入，因此传入的参数不需要额外转义特殊字符。基本上可以满足所有的数据库操作，而且在所有支持的数据库系统上都可以执行。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); text-transform: none; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); text-transform: none; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">1.使用查询构造器实现增删改查</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); text-transform: none; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">同样在Student控制器里测试以下代码：</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); text-transform: none; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\">（</span>1）新增</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); text-transform: none; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p><p><strong style=\"outline: 0px; font-weight: bold; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\">[php]</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a title=\"view plain\" class=\"ViewSource\" style=\"background-position: left top; margin: 0px 10px 0px 0px; padding: 1px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; width: 16px; height: 16px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-indent: -2000px; font-size: 9px; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; cursor: pointer; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-image: url(&quot;https://csdnimg.cn/release/phoenix/images/ico_plain.gif&quot;); background-repeat: no-repeat; background-color: inherit;\" href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/zls986992484/article/details/52824962#\">view plain</a><span style=\"outline: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a title=\"copy\" class=\"CopyToClipboard\" style=\"background-position: left top; margin: 0px 10px 0px 0px; padding: 1px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; width: 16px; height: 16px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-indent: -2000px; font-size: 9px; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; cursor: pointer; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-image: url(&quot;https://csdnimg.cn/release/phoenix/images/ico_copy.gif&quot;); background-repeat: no-repeat; background-color: inherit;\" href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/zls986992484/article/details/52824962#\">copy</a></span><span style=\"outline: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\"></span></p><ol class=\"dp-c list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\"><li><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: black; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\"><span class=\"vars\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(221, 0, 0); -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">$bool</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: black; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">=DB::table(</span><span class=\"string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: blue; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">&quot;vipinfo&quot;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: black; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">)-&gt;insert([</span><span class=\"string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: blue; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">&#39;vip_ID&#39;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: black; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">=&gt;6,</span><span class=\"string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: blue; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">&#39;vip_name&#39;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: black; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: blue; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">&#39;zls&#39;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: black; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">,</span><span class=\"string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: blue; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">&#39;vip_type&#39;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: black; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: blue; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">&quot;出行&quot;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: black; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">,</span><span class=\"string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: blue; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">&#39;vip_fenshu&#39;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: black; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: inherit;\">=&gt;800]);&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"margin: 0px;